description: You just gotta check out Silver Moon Taqueria, Utah’s first truck to serve fish tacos, which happen to be absolutely delish.This celestial blue truck offers a savory selection of Summer Salads, Tacos, and Quesadillas with your choice of succulent grilled fish, juicy marinated chicken, or tangy hand-trimmed steak. Add in a variety of incredibly flavorful homemade salsas, and one bite of this incredible fare will send you straight over the moon. Orbit on over to Silver Moon Taqueria for Mexican food that’s so tasty, it’s out of this world.
name: Silver Moon Taqueria
